VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)\bSELECT\b.*\bFROM\b.*\bWHERE\b.*\+.*\+
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(?i)\b(input|request|param|query|\$_GET|\$_POST|\$_REQUEST)\b
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects SQL queries with unsafe string concatenation of user input.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure SQL Query: Unsafe String Concatenation.
